data.description: Tucked away in quiet Ashely Estates, this beautiful home is just what you’re looking for.  Cozy up to the wood burning fireplace in the warm and inviting family room which offers plenty of space to entertain your guests.  Host a dinner party in your lovely dining room just off the large kitchen which has plenty of cabinets, beautiful stainless appliances, and gorgeous countertops.  This home also offers a split bedroom plan with a spacious master ensuite and three roomy bedrooms.  A large laundry room offers excess storage.  The backyard is sizable, fenced in and there is plenty of room for parking.  Ashely Estates is located in West Mobile off Schillinger Road.  7330 Tara Dr. S. is nestled in the back of the neighborhood.
